%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20a%20Montessori%20school%20director%20and%20a%20mom%2C%20I%20know%20an%20app%20can't%20replace%20a%20village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20adult%20mother%20sitting%20with%20her%20baby%20in%20bedroom%20and%20looking%20at%20phone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67192bb701ea6d83dee380ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20sees%20how%20parenting%20apps%20don't%20replace%20a%20village%20and%20can%20alienate%20new%20parents.%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20Durmaz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBaby-tracking%20apps%20are%20becoming%20more%20popular%2C%20especially%20for%20first-time%20parents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20mom%20and%20educator%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20parents%20need%20more%20authentic%20connections%20than%20information.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20no%20one-size-fits-all%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20raising%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2012%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20found%20a%20rudimentary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-parenting-and-pregnancy-apps-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapp%20that%20helped%20me%20track%20how%20often%20and%20for%20how%20long%20I%20fed%20my%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20told%20my%20mom%20about%20it%2C%20excited%20to%20share%20how%20advanced%20things%20had%20gotten%20since%20her%20days%20of%20feeding%20babies.%20My%20mom%20responded%20matter-of-factly%2C%20%26quot%3BHoney%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20all%20that.%20Just%20let%20the%20baby%20nurse%20when%20she's%20hungry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnnoyed%20at%20her%20dismissiveness%2C%20I%20asked%20a%20seemingly%20obvious%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20will%20I%20know%20when%20she's%20hungry%3F%26quot%3B%20She%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BBabies%20are%20pretty%20good%20at%20letting%20you%20know%20things%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20she%20was%20right.%20I%20ended%20up%20deleting%20the%20app%20after%20realizing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-doesnt-use-baby-monitor-no-anxiety-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20baby%20was%20an%20expert%20at%20making%20her%20needs%20known%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20relieving%20myself%20of%20data%20collection%2C%20I%20was%20lucky%20to%20have%20my%20first%20seed%20of%20skepticism%20regarding%20parenting%20and%20technology%20firmly%20planted%20in%20my%20mind.%20I%20went%20on%20to%20have%20three%20more%20kids%2C%20and%20while%20I%20surely%20Googled%20things%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20I%20stayed%20out%20of%20the%20whole%20baby%20tracking%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2bccd93-0cd4-4ecf-b948-94e0b4d80bfd%5C%22%3EMy%20friends%20tell%20me%20about%20all%20the%20apps%20they%20use%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20several%20of%20my%20friends%20have%20had%20babies.%20They%20tell%20me%20about%20the%20apps%20they%20use%20to%20track%20developmental%20milestones%2C%20nap%20schedules%2C%20duration%20of%20those%20naps%2C%20every%20ounce%20of%20liquid%20that%20goes%20into%20the%20baby's%20body%2C%20and%20every%20bit%20of%20excrement%20that%20comes%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20friends%2C%20all%20new%20moms%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20love%2Fhate%20relationship%20with%20their%20baby-tracking%20apps.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20they%20feel%20validated%20and%20reassured%20to%20have%20all%20this%20data%20in%20their%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20irrefutable%20evidence%20of%20attentive%20parenting.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20know%20something%20feels%20off%20about%20the%20whole%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20app%20knows%20more%20about%20their%20day-to-day%20existence%20and%20that%20of%20their%20baby%20than%20their%20own%20partners.%20They%20wonder%20aloud%20if%20their%20apps%20are%20providing%20them%20support%20or%20an%20unhealthy%20sense%20of%20isolation%20and%20high-stakes%20thinking.%20As%20a%20mom%20and%20an%20educator%20who%20began%20teaching%20before%20the%20iPhone%20was%20invented%2C%20I%20don't%20wonder%20quite%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272903342-341b-477b-b827-b51ddfba967e%5C%22%3EParents%20are%20more%20isolated%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20late%2019th%20and%20early%2020th%20centuries%2C%20there%20was%20optimism%20that%20technology%20in%20the%20form%20of%20household%20appliances%20would%20reduce%20the%20heavy%20burden%20on%20homemakers.%20However%2C%20the%20net%20effect%20of%20conveniences%20like%20washing%20machines%2C%20vacuums%2C%20and%20electric%20irons%20was%20not%20all%20ease.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Nicholas%20Carr%2C%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Switch%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20in%20the%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20psychic%20price%20of%20the%20new%20tools%20and%20the%20new%20roles%20they%20engendered%20was%20sometimes%20high.%20Adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20many%2C%20electrification%20brought%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20alienation%20and%20loneliness%20into%20the%20home.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20help%20but%20notice%20the%20recent%20proliferation%20of%20social%20media%20and%20app-based%20technology%20in%20the%20parenting%20sphere%20has%20had%20a%20similar%20impact%20on%20parents.%20The%20elusive%20promise%20of%20more%20ease%20and%20free%20time%20for%20social%20connection%20has%20instead%20led%20to%20more%20isolation%2C%20less%20community%20support%2C%20and%20increased%20societal%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20apps%20that%20don't%20just%20help%20parents%20track%20the%20minutiae%20of%20baby%20care%20but%20rather%20track%20the%20practice%20of%20parenting%20young%20children.%20Some%20apps%20promise%20to%20guide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccept-big-feelings-little-kids-normalize-same-for-parents-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparents%20toward%20raising%20well-adjusted%20ki