5fdda234af076d3cf92e655%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221930%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnly%20the%20most%20loyal%20North%20Koreans%20are%20allowed%20senior%20positions%20in%20the%20army.%20%3Cp%3EKCNA%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20North%20Korean%20state%20also%20has%20harsher%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emeans%20to%20keep%20its%20citizens%20abroad%20in%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bruce%20W.%20Bennett%2C%20a%20defense%20researcher%20and%20North%20Korea%20specialist%20at%20RAND%2C%20those%20who%20leave%2C%20like%20diplomats%2C%20are%20almost%20never%20allowed%20to%20bring%20their%20whole%20family%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20typical%20for%20the%20Kims%20to%20insist%20that%20at%20least%20one%20member%20of%20any%20family%20operating%20overseas%20remain%20in%20Pyongyang%20as%20a%20hostage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20anyone%20who%20does%20defect%20ensures%20that%20their%20whole%20family%20suffers%2C%20Bermudez%20said.%20%26quot%3BNorth%20Korea%20believes%20in%20generational%20punishment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20interviews%20with%20escapees%20and%20defectors%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20greatest%20sorrows%20that%20they%20have%20is%20that%20they've%20left%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20their%20extended%20family%20would%20likely%20be%20sent%20to%20brutal%20work%20camps%20%E2%80%94%20described%20by%20Bermudez%20described%20as%20similar%20to%20a%20Nazi%20work%20camp%20or%20a%20Soviet%20gulag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266250527-728a-4d38-9302-d9af1004c7d9%5C%22%3EAn%20opportunity%20for%20the%20West%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bscared%20to%20death%26quot%3B%20of%20information%20being%20brought%20back%20to%20North%20Korea%20from%20abroad%2C%20Bennett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20rails%20against%20culture%20from%20the%20outside%20world%20%E2%80%94%20like%20in%2