ips%20with%20suppliers%2C%20vast%20scale%20in%20grocery%20retailing%2C%20and%20innovations%20such%20as%20the%20Walmart%2B%20subscription%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22exterior%20of%20a%20walmart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66df3d205444ffafa763c24f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223109%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalmart%20has%20enormous%20purchasing%20power%2C%20letting%20it%20keep%20prices%20low.%3Cp%3EAlexanderstock23%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c237c42e-eee2-4359-abf8-7b50afd3e99c%5C%22%3EFamily%20fortunes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Walton%20shrewdly%20structured%20his%20fledgling%20company%20as%20a%20family%20partnership%20in%201953%2C%20giving%2020%25%20stakes%20to%20each%20of%20his%20four%20children.%20Put%20differently%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalton-family-sam-walmart-stock-billionaires-estate-planning-inheritance-wealth-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehanded%2080%25%20of%20Walmart%20to%20his%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20was%20worth%20next%20to%20nothing%2C%20sparing%20them%20from%20paying%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20estate%20taxes%20to%20inherit%20his%20stock%20after%20he%20died%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKing%20told%20BI%20he%20wasn't%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20Waltons%20near%20the%20top%20of%20a%20rich%20list%20dominated%20by%20technology%20bosses%20like%20Musk%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWalmart%20is%20a%20family%20firm%20that%20is%20in%20its%20second%20generation%2C%20or%20the%20initial%20value%20created%20by%20Sam%20Walton%20has%20not%20been%20split%20across%20multiple%20heirs%2C%26quot%3B%20King%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20John%20T.%20Walton's%20son%2C%20Lukas%20Walton%2C%20ranks%20in%20the%20top%2050%20of%20Bloomberg's%20wealth%20index%20with%20a%20nearly%20%2437%20billion%20f