0People%20love%20this.%20He%20is%20the%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20had%20a%20message%20for%20the%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20of%20BJP-Sena-NCP%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20most%20corrupt%2C%20you%20should%20be%20thrown%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20supporters%20took%20part%20in%20a%20massive%20rally%20to%20accompany%20the%20junior%20Thackeray%20for%20the%20filing%20of%20his%20nomination%20papers.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%2034-year-old%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20here%20for%20the%20best%20wishes%20of%20the%20people%20and%20to%20win%20the%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20Thackeray%20won%20the%20Worli%20seat%20in%20the%202019%20election%20and%20served%20as%20a%20state%20minister%20before%20his%20father's%20government%20was%20toppled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20votes%20on%20November%2020%20and%20the%20counting%20is%20on%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729758720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F5e4pv9eo_arvind-sawant-interview_625x300_24_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-election-sena-ubt-seat-sharing-differences-not-dispute-thackeray-sena-leader-on-india-bloc-6862406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Differences%20over%20seat-sharing%20cannot%20be%20considered%20disputes%2C%20senior%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Arvind%20Sawant%20told%20NDTV%20today%2C%20stressing%20that%20there%20is%20no%20rift%20in%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%20as%20it%20gears%20up%20for%20the%20significant%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-election-sena-ubt-seat-sharing-differences-not-dispute-thackeray-sena-leader-on-india-bloc-6862406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New-Gen%20KTM%20390%20Adventure