0to%20be.%20It's%20the%20journey%20between%20those%20two%20dates%20that%20has%20come%20to%20define%20the%20chequered%20legacy%20of%20the%2046th%20President%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20credibility%20has%20gone%20up%20in%20flames%20in%20West%20Asia%20and%20he%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20leaving%20behind%20a%20dark%20legacy%20that%20his%20successor%20would%20try%20to%20erase%20from%20the%20pages%20of%20history.%20But%20his%20failures%20on%20other%20issues%20have%20also%20been%20shocking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20let's%20start%20with%20his%20sunshine%20moments%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Hero's%20Welcome%20In%20Germany%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Friday%2C%20Biden%20tiptoed%20into%20Germany%2C%20almost%20unnoticed%2C%20to%20receive%20the%20country's%20highest%20civilian%20award%20for%20his%20contribution%20to%20trans-Atlantic%20relations.%20The%20world's%20most%20powerful%20leader%20shuffled%20along%20next%20to%20German%20President%20Frank-Walter%20Steinmeier%3B%20their%20slow%2C%20tentative%20steps%20felt%20as%20though%20a%20ghostly%20presence%20was%20tagging%20along%E2%80%94a%20moment%20straight%20out%20of%20T.S.%20Eliot's%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Waste%20Land%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20the%20third%20who%20always%20walks%20beside%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20farewell%20visit%20to%20Germany%20comes%20with%20a%20cloud%20of%20unease%20looming%20over%20Europe.%20The%20spectre%20of%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20their%20%E2%80%98tormentor-in-chief'%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20%C2%A0possibly%20returning%20to%20power%20has%20made%20Berlin%20and%20Europe%20jittery.%20They%20remember%20Trump's%20views%20on%20NATO%20all%20too%20well%2C%20which%20had%20left%20the%20European%20members%20wondering%20whether%20the%20US%20was%20serious%20about%20protecting%20Europe%20against%20a%20potential%20Russian%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elusive%20third%20figure%20in%20Eliot's%20poem%20could%20just%20be%20Europe's%20collective%20dread%20of%20a%20Trump%20redux.%20Steinmeier%20still%20carries%20the%20scars%20from%20those%20years%20(2016-2020)%2C%20recalling%20a%20time%20when%20the%20US-Europe%20bond%20was%20fraying.%20%26quot%3B...just%20a%20handful%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20distance%20had%20grown%20so%20wide%20that%20we%20almost%20lost%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reminisced.%20Thankfully%2C%20to%20Germany%20and%20Europe's%20collective%20relief%2C%20Biden%20was%20quick%20to%20restore%20Europe's%20faith%20in%20the%20trans-Atlantic%20alliance%20%E2%80%9Cliterally%20overnight%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20the%20German%20President%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurely%2C%20Biden's%20European%20outreach%20and%20climate%20action%20were%20two%20of%20the%20very%20few%20successes%20of%20his%20presidency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden%2C%20Blinken%20and%20Bibi%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Israel%20continues%20to%20pound%20Lebanon%20and%20Gaza%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20glaringly%20obvious%3A%20the%20US%20influence%20on%20Israeli%20decision-making%20has%20been%20greatly%20cut%20down%20since%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks.%20Sure%2C%20Israel's%20military%20might%20squash%20terrorist%20threats%20for%20now.%20But%20lasting%20peace%3F%20That's%20unlikely%20and%20uncertain.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%2C%20Antony%20Blinken%2C%20is%20in%20West%20Asia%20again%2C%20but%20he%2C%20like%20his%20boss%2C%20is%20taken%20seriously%20neither%20by%20Benjamin%20aka%20%E2%80%98Bibi'%20Netanyahu%20nor%20by%20Arab%20allies.%20Biden%20has%20lost%20his%20credibility%20in%20the%20region%20as%20an%20honest%20peace%20broker%20largely%20due%20to%20his%20weak%20handling%20of%20Netanyahu%20and%20letting%20daily%20massacres%20in%20the%20region%20continue.%20If%20war%20breaks%20out%20in%20West%20Asia%2C%20Biden%20might%20just%20hand%20Kamala%20Harris's%20campaign%20its%20own%20little%20farewell%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20had%20at%20least%20got%20Israel%20to%20sign%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%20Peace%20Agreement%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%2C%20Bahrain%20and%20Morocco.%20These%20agreements%20aimed%20to%20normalise%20diplomatic%20relations%2C%20expand%20economic%20cooperation%2C%20and%20promote%20regional%20peace%20and%20stability.%20What%20does%20Biden%20have%20to%20show%20for%3F%20The%20deal%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia%20was%20almost%20ready%20to%20be%20signed%2C%20but%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20pushed%20it%20back.%20And%20so%20far%2C%20Biden%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20persuade%20the%20warring%20parties%20to%20come%20to%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbraham%20Accords%2C%20A%20Flawed%20Trump%20Legacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Abraham%20Accords%20had%20come%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20West%20Asia.%20I%20even%20remember%20watching%20an%20interview%20with%20American-Israeli%20rabbi%20Yaakov%20Israel%20Herzog%2C%20who%20had%20parked%20himself%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20boldly%20declaring%20his%20plan%20to%20open%20the%20first%20Jewish%20community%20centre%20in%20Riyadh.%20Saudi%20rulers%20just%20pretended%20not%20to%20notice.%20Everyone%20assumed%20the%20peace%20deal%20with%20Israel%20was%20practically%20signed%2C%20sealed%2C%20and%20delivered.%20Jews%20visiting%20the%20Kingdom%3F%20That%20was%20almost%20possible%2C%20and%20it%20would%20have%20been%20some%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20here's%20the%20thing%E2%80%94the%20Abraham%20Accords%20had%20overlooked%20the%20Palestinian%20issue.%20Normalising%20relations%20without%20even%20mentioning%20Palestinian%20self-determination%20was%2C%20in%20hindsight%2C%20unwise.%20That's%20a%20recipe%20for%20fragile%20peace.%20The%20real%20issues%E2%80%94borders%2C%20settlements%2C%20Jerusalem%2C%20refugees%E2%80%94were%20left%20out%20of%20purview.%20And%20let's%20not%20forget%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20leadership%20wasn't%20even%20invited%20to%20the%20table.%20A%20peace%20deal%20without%20the%20main%20player%20was%20myopic%2C%20at%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGranted%20that%20Biden%20inherited%20a%20diplomatic%20mess%20and%20an%20uphill%20battle.%20He%20was%20supposed%20to%20dive%20into%20the%20deep%20end%2C%20fix%20the%20flaws%20in%20the%20Accords%20and%20put%20the%20Palestinian%20issue%20back%20on%20the%20agenda.%20But%20he%20didn't.%20The%20result%20was%20Hamas's%20deadly%20October%20attack.%20Now%2C%20the%20world%20has%20been%20left%20calling%2C%20once%20again%2C%20for%20a%20renewed%20focus%20on%20Palestinian%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Host%20Of%20Other%20Failures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhoever%20gets%20the%20keys%20to%20the%20White%20House%20next%20will%20inherit%20the%20dilemma%20of%20either%20trying%20to%20bring%20order%20to%20West%20Asia%2C%20which%20could%20overshadow%20US%20priorities%20in%20Europe%20and%20China%2C%20or%20dealing%20with%20all%20the%20Biden%20failings%20simultaneously.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20Biden's%20legacy%20in%20West%20Asia%20is%20in%20tatters%3B%20it%20carries%20the%20baggage%20of%20extreme%20violence%2C%20death%20and%20destruction.%20Thousands%20have%20died%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20millions%20have%20been%20rendered%20homeless%2C%20and%20a%20big%20number%20have%20migrated%20to%20safer%20countries.%20The%20Israelis%2C%20escaping%20the%20war%2C%20have%20been%20flooding%20into%20Cyprus.%20Many%20in%20the%20region%20believe%20it%20will%20take%20generations%20for%20the%20scars%20to%20be%20erased.%20One%20wonders%20whether%20Biden%20will%20ever%20reflect%20on%20his%20failures%20once%20he%20leaves%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20approach%20to%20China%20has%20also%20faced%20scrutiny.%20His%20administration's%20efforts%20to%20establish%20a%20coalition%20of%20like-minded%20nations%2C%20which%20included%20India%2C%20have%20yielded%20mixed%20results.%20The%20Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%20for%20Prosperity%20(IPEF)%20and%20the%20Quad%20security%20dialogue%20have%20been%20touted%20as%20key%20initiatives%2C%20but%20their%20effectiveness%20remains%20uncertain.%20China's%20growing%20economic%20and%20military%20influence%20has%20significant%20implications%20for%20global%20governance%20and%20regional%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUkraine%3A%20Pumping%20In%20Money%20Without%20A%20Goal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainians%20are%20dreading%20Donald%20Trump%3B's%20possible%20return%20to%20power%20because%20he%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20he%20would%20strike%20a%20peace%20deal%20with%20Russia.%20He%20is%20also%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20US%20pumping%20in%20billions%20of%20dollars%20and%20sending%20plane-loads%20of%20weapons%20to%20Ukraine.%20The%20Ukrainians%20would%20thus%20like%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20President%2C%20as%20they%20believe%20she%20will%20carry%20on%20defending%20Ukraine%20and%20continue%20to%20help%20it%20with%20cash%20and%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Biden%2C%20Pax%20Americana%2C%20the%20era%20of%20America-led%20global%20order%2C%20has%20been%20showing%20clear%20signs%20of%20decline.%20From%20the%20chaotic%20withdrawal%20from%20Afghanistan%20to%20the%20US's%20impotency%20in%20West%20Asia%2C%20Biden's%20foreign%20policy%20has%20often%20been%20seen%20as%20reactive%20rather%20than%20proactive.%20The%20cowardly%20pullout%20from%20Kabul%20in%202021%2C%20which%20left%20behind%20chaos%20and%20emboldened%20the%20Taliban%2C%20sent%20a%20message%20that%20US%20military%20power%20no%20longer%20guarantees%20stability%20in%20the%20regions%20it%20occupies.%20This%20failure%2C%20followed%20by%20Washington's%20inconsistent%20handling%20of%20alliances%2C%20signalled%20a%20retreat%20from%20the%20role%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98global%20enforcer'%20that%20the%20US%20has%20played%20since%20World%20War%20II.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20China-Russia%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20Biden's%20response%20to%20the%20rising%20influence%20of%20China%20and%20Russia%20has%20been%20less%20than%20robust%2C%20weakening%20American%20hegemony.%20While%20efforts%20like%20the%20Quad%20alliances%20aim%20to%20counterbalance%20China's%20assertiveness%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20Beijing%20continues%20to%20expand%20its%20influence%20through%20economic%20investments%2C%20military%20posturing%2C%20and%20diplomatic%20and%20multilateral%20efforts%20such%20as%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20and%20BRICS.%20Simultaneously%2C%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20has%20drawn%20attention%20to%20the%20limits%20of%20US%20deterrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20of%20Pax%20Americana%20may%20not%20have%20started%20under%20Biden%2C%20but%20it%20certainly%20accelerated%20under%20him.%20Domestically%2C%20Biden's%20presidency%20has%20focused%20on%20economic%20recovery%2C%20social%20justice%2C%20and%20climate%20action.%20The%20American%20Rescue%20Plan%20and%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20have%20helped%20stabilise%20the%20economy%20and%20address%20social%20issues%20to%20some%20extent.%20However%2C%20bipartisan%20cooperation%20has%20been%20more%20elusive%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20many%20of%20Biden's%20initiatives%20have%20faced%20resistance%20from%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Donald%20Trump%20wins%20on%20November%205%2C%20Biden's%20legacy%20could%20be%20swept%20into%20the%20dustbin%20of%20history.%20But%20if%20Kamala%20Harris%20comes%20out%20on%20top%2C%20she%20will%20have%20to%20work%20very%20hard%20to%20salvage%20it%E2%80%94while%20defining%20her%20own%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729758180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fvc