%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20expelled%20the%2032-year-old%20leader%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20cross-voting%20during%20the%20Maharashtra%20legislative%20council%20election.%20Mr%20Siddique%20had%20denied%20the%20charge.%20The%20young%20leader%20is%20the%20son%20of%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20faction)%20leader%20and%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Sidiqqui%2C%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20old%20friends%20have%20announced%20their%20candidates%20from%20Vandre%20East.%20Supporting%20was%20never%20in%20their%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BMaintain%20relations%20with%20those%20who%20give%20respect%2C%20no%20point%20in%20surrounding%20yourself%20with%20a%20crowd%2C%20now%20the%20people%20will%20decide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20Zeeshan%20Siddiqui%20defeated%20the%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Vishwanath%20Mahadeshwar%2C%20former%20Mayor%20of%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20to%20win%20Vandre%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vandre%20East%20seat%20has%20gone%20to%20Congress%20ally%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20as%20part%20of%20seat-sharing%20within%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20has%20named%20Varun%20Sardesai%20as%20its%20candidate.%20Varun%20Sardesai%20is%20the%20nephew%20of%20party%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Vandre%20East%20seat%20has%20gone%20to%20NCP's%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20as%20part%20of%20seat-sharing%20within%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20bloc.%20While%20the%20NCP%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20candidate%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20field%20Zeeshan%20Siddiqui%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20sympathy%20wave%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20his%20father's%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Siddiqui%2C%2066%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20Zeeshan%20Siddique's%20office%20in%20Bandra%20on%20Octo