he%20statue%20of%20Lady%20Justice%20without%20consultation%20with%20the%20Bar.%20We%20are%20equal%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20administration%20of%20justice%20but%20these%20changes%20when%20proposed%2C%20were%20never%20brought%20to%20our%20attention.%20We%20are%20totally%20clueless%20on%20the%20rationale%20behind%20these%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20resolution%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20a%20museum%20has%20apparently%20been%20proposed%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20Judges%20Library%20whereas%20we%20had%20demanded%20a%20Library%2C%20Cafe%20cum%20Lounge%20for%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bar%20as%20the%20present%20cafeteria%20is%20inadequate%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bar.%20We%20are%20concerned%20that%20despite%20our%20objection%20raised%20against%20the%20proposed%20Museum%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20Judges%20library%2C%20work%20has%20started%20for%20the%20museum%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20resolution%2C%20signed%20by%20Mr%20Sibal%20and%20other%20office-bearers%20of%20the%20lawyers'%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20unanimously%20oppose%20the%20proposed%20museum%20in%20the%20High%20Security%20Zone%20and%20press%20our%20demand%20for%20a%20Library%20and%20a%20Cafe%20cum%20Lounge%20for%20our%20members%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20Lady%20Justice%20statue%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20blindfold%20has%20come%20off%20and%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20has%20replaced%20the%20sword%20in%20her%20left%20hand.%20The%20blindfold's%20removal%20is%20aimed%20at%20sending%20a%20message%20that%20the%20law%20in%20the%20country%20is%20not%20blind%2C%20while%20the%20sword%20was%20replaced%20because%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lady%20Justice%20statue%2C%20found%20at%20courts%20across%20the%20world%2C%20carries%20scales%20symbolising%20balance%2C%20has%20a%20blindfold%20symbolising%20impartiality%20and%20holds%20a%20sword%20suggesting%20that%20justice%20is%20swift%20and%20final.%20Several%20countries%20have%20made%20changes%20to%20this%20statue%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20associated%20with%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud's%20office%2C%20he%20believes%20that%20India%20should%20move%20on%20from%20the%20British%20legacy%20and%20that%20law%20is%20never%20blind%2C%20but%20sees%20everyone%20equally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20that%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Lady%20of%20Justice%20should%20be%20changed.%20He%20said%20the%20statue%20should%20have%20the%20Constitution%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20not%20a%20sword%2C%20so%20that%20a%20message%20goes%20out%20to%20the%20country%20that%20she%20dispenses%20justice%20according%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20sword%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20violence%20but%20courts%20deliver%20justice%20according%20to%20constitutional%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scales%20in%20the%20right%20hand%2C%20the%20source%20said%2C%20have%20been%20retained%20because%20they%20represent%20balance%20in%20society%20and%20symbolise%20courts%20weighing%20arguments%20from%20both%20sides%20before%20delivering%20a%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20has%20a%20new%20emblem%20and%20flag.%20The%20blue%20flag%20displays%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20building%20and%20the%20Constitution.%20It%20has%20the%20Sanskrit%20verse%20'Yato%20Dharmastato%20Jai'%20--%20meaning%20'Where%20there%20is%20Dharma%2C%20there%20is%20victory'%20--%20written%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729747260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fdvfhspg8_new-lady-of-justice-statue-supreme-court_625x300_16_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-bar-association-clueless-on-rationale-top-court-lawyers-body-on-new-lady-justice-statue-6861126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22T