udent%20dropout%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20school%20was%20upgraded%20to%20an%20upper%20primary%20school%3B%20that%20same%20year%2C%20Indrakumar%20received%20the%20National%20Teachers%20Award%20for%20his%20contributions%20to%20primary%20education.%20However%2C%20the%20problem%20of%20students%20dropping%20out%20at%20such%20young%20ages%20continued%20to%20trouble%20him%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20seek%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20called%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20children%20studying%20in%20my%20school.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20dropping%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20boarding%20facility%2C%20but%20I%20needed%20monetary%20help%20to%20run%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FEducation%2FSupport-Indrakumar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FEducation%2FSupport-Indrakumar%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20a%20monthly%20fee%20was%20decided%20for%20the%20resident%20students.%20The%20hostel%20began%20with%20one%20warden%20and%2028%20students.%20Currently%2C%20the%20facility%20houses%20three%20wardens%2C%20who%20also%20teach%20at%20Kumbi%20Sandhong%20Upper%20Primary%20School%2C%20and%20caters%20to%2075%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20boarding%20facility%2C%20Indrakumar%20launched%20his%20Sunday%20lessons%2C%20which%20culminated%20in%20campaigns%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363139%2Fjai-dhar-gupta-vijay-dhasmana-biosphere-rajaji-national-park-uttarakhand-rewilding-forest-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmental%20awareness%20and%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lessons%20were%20started%20as%20an%20initiative%20to%20broaden%20the%20perspectives%20of%20students%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20Supported%20by%20district%20education%20officials%2C%20students%20are%20taught%20local%20lessons%20outside%20their%20textbooks%20each%20week.%20Topics%20include%20the%20history%20and%20demography%20of%20Manipur%2C%20the%20role%20of%20Loktak%20Lake%20in%20maintaining%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20Sangai%20(an%20endangered%20subspecies%20of%20Eld%E2%80%99s%20deer%20found%20only%20in%20Manipur).%20The%20classes%20are%20conducted%20by%20guest%20speakers%20ranging%20from%20corporate%20professionals%20to%20psychological%20counsellors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndrakumar%20also%20uses%20his%20Sundays%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20sustainable%20practices%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368964%2Fthe-body-shop-plastics-for-change-use-recycled-plastic-in-product-packaging-empower-waste-collectors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-02-at-11.40.00-AM-1_11zon-1729604175.jpeg%3Fresize%3D2058%252C927%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222058%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khagembam%20Indrakumar%20Singh%20and%20his%20students%20participate%20in%20a%20cleanup%20drive.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-02-at-11.40.00-AM-1_11zon-1729604175.jpeg%3Fw%3D2058%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%202058w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-02-at-11.40.00-AM-1_11zon-1729604175.jp