agement%22%3A130%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fliam-payne-toxicology-report-not-complete-argentina-authorities-say-after-claim-cocaine-found-in-his-body-13238894%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fliam-payne-toxicology-report-not-complete-argentina-authorities-say-after-claim-cocaine-found-in-his-body-13238894%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fliam-payne-toxicology-report-not-complete-argentina-authorities-say-after-claim-cocaine-found-in-his-body-13238894%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Conservationists%20Who%20Have%20Dedicated%20Their%20Lives%20to%20Protecting%20Snow%20Leopards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fwildlife-biodiversity%2Findia-has-718-snow-leopards-most-of-them-live-in-unprotected-areas-centre-94174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20other%20non-profit%20organisations%20on%2030%20January%202024%2C%20there%20are%20just%20718%20snow%20leopards%20in%20India%2C%20of%20which%20only%20a%20third%20are%20under%20legal%20protection.%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EStatus%20Report%20of%20Snow%20Leopards%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20that%20barely%2034%25%20of%20the%201%2C20%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20snow%20leopard%20habitat%20in%20India%20is%20legally%20protected.%20Less%20than%2070%25%20of%20this%20predator%E2%80%99s%20habitat%20remains%20unprotected.%20%3Cem%3E(Above%20images%20of%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20a%20snow%20leopard%20%26amp%3B%20Charudutt%20Mishra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20figures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20for%20local%20communities%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20the%20conservation%20of%20this%20threatened%20species.%20Here%20are%20eight%20conservationists%20who%20have%20done%20incredible%20work%20in%20not%20only%20understanding%20snow%20leopards%20but%20also%20engaging%20local%20communities%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%20(Charu)%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%2C%20is%20considered%20by%20many%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20expert%20on%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20pioneer%20of%20the%20community-based%20conservation%20model%20and%20has%20spent%20nearly%20three%20decades%20spearheading%20groundbreaking%20projects.%20In%201997%2C%20he%20embarked%20upon%20a%20PhD%20in%20the%20remote%20village%20of%20Kibber%2C%20in%20Spiti%20Valley%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20Upon%20reaching%20there%2C%20he%20heard%20a%20disturbing%20story%20that%20a%20snow%20leopard%20had%20recently%20been%20mercilessly%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20letting%20anger%20or%20distrust%20get%20in%20the%20way%2C%20Charu%20immersed%20himself%20in%20the%20community%20and%20took%20the%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20hardships%20under%20which%20they%20lived.%20He%20learnt%20that%20local%20communities%20were%20not%20unwilling%20but%20unable%20to%20%E2%80%9Cactually%20participate%20in%20conservation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snow%20Leopard%20(Images%20courtesy%20Karamjeet%20Singh%2FX)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3