%3EKaramjeet%20Singh%2FX%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Whitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729608170000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20International%20Snow%20Leopard%20Day%2C%20we%20highlight%20the%20contributions%20of%20eight%20conservationists%20who%20have%20dedicated%20their%20lives%20to%20protecting%20this%20elusive%20wild%20cat%20by%20ethically%20and%20effectively%20engaging%20with%20local%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371701%2Finternational-snow-leopard-day-conservationists-in-india-charudutt-mishra-tsewang-namgail%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20Techie%20Turns%20Organic%20Farmer%2C%20Builds%20a%20Profitable%20Moringa%20Business%20With%20His%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20over%20two%20decades%20that%20Jitender%20Mann%20spent%20in%20cities%20like%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Delhi%2C%20he%20observed%20a%20concerning%20trend%3A%20rising%20rates%20of%20health%20issues%20among%20both%20young%20and%20elderly%20residents%3B%20thyroid%20disorders%20and%20high%20blood%20pressure%20appeared%20to%20Jitender%20as%20a%20common%20occurrence%20in%20urban%20areas.%20He%2C%20himself%2C%20was%20no%20exception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20workaholic%20during%20my%20early%2020s%2C%20often%20being%20the%20last%20one%20to%20leave%20office%20at%201%20am.%20By%20my%20early%2040s%2C%20I%20was%20suffering%20from%20high%20blood%20pressure%20(BP)%20and%20extreme%20joint%20pains.%20I%20would%20commute%20via%20the%20metro%20and%20sit%20all%20day%20at%20a%20desk.%20I%20felt%20healthy%2C%20but%20once%20I%20started%20medication%20for%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20I%20realised%20I%20was%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20blood%20pressure%20was%20160.%20It%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20me.%20After%20starting%20the%20medication%2C%20I%20felt%20that%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20my%20new%20normal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20the%20Laxmi%20Nagar%20area%20near%20the%20Yamuna%20river%2C%20he%20often%20witnessed%20farmers%20using%20polluted%20water%20to%20irrigate%20their%20fields.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20Delhi%20consumes%20food%20produced%20in%20those%20fields.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20only%20a%20few%20elderly%20people%20would%20complain%20of%20joint%20pains%2C%20but%20these%20days%2C%20even%20young%20people%20and%20toddlers%20are%20experiencing%20blood%20glucose%20issues.%20I%20am%20not%20an%20expert%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20everything%20is%20related%20to%20the%20food%20we%20eat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jitender%20and%20Sarla%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2