gourd%2C%20and%20moringa%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImpressed%20by%20the%20results%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20replace%20their%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20fields%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303221%2Fkerala-engineer-turned-farmer-starts-moringa-mango-organic-farm-in-melbourne-australia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoringa%20farm%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20moving%20to%20their%20village.%20Starting%20with%20two%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20the%20couple%20gradually%20expanded%20their%20production%20to%20four%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20titled%20%E2%80%98Moringa%20oleifera%3A%20An%20Updated%20Comprehensive%20Review%20of%20Its%20Pharmacological%20Activities%2C%20Ethnomedicinal%2C%20Phytopharmaceutical%20Formulation%2C%20Clinical%2C%20Phytochemical%2C%20and%20Toxicological%20Aspects%E2%80%99%2C%20published%20in%20PubMed%20Central%20(PMC)%2C%20observed%20that%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282661%2Fkerala-woman-entrepreneur-makes-healthy-millet-flour-from-moringa-jackfruit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20moringa%20oleifera%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctree%20of%20life%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%20tree%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20was%20effective%20in%20treating%20wounds%2C%20pain%2C%20ulcers%2C%20liver%20disease%2C%20heart%20disease%2C%20cancer%2C%20and%20inflammation%3B%20it%20was%20also%20proved%20to%20be%20beneficial%20in%20lowering%20glucose%20levels.%20As%20per%20the%20same%20study%2C%20moringa%20leaves%20are%20a%20quick%20remedy%20for%20inflammatory%20conditions%20such%20as%20glandular%20inflammation%2C%20headache%2C%20and%20bronchitis.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20miraculous%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20exclaims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000p