abilities%2C%20and%20students%20pitch%20stories%20and%20win%20cash%20prizes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371208%2Fias-sakshi-sawhney-runs-future-tycoons-challenge-to-help-marginalised-punjab-people-become-entrepreneurs-shark-tank%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jackfruit%20Helped%20This%2057-YO%20Homemaker%20Build%20a%20Rs%208%20Lakh%2FYr%20Business%2C%20%E2%80%98Eden%20Jackfruit%20Products%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20of%20Idukki%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Rani%20Sunny%20spends%20her%20days%20surrounded%20by%20the%20lush%20greenery%20of%20cardamom%20and%20jackfruit%20plantations%20spread%20across%204.5%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20her%20backyard.%20While%20her%20family%20harvested%20cardamom%2C%20they%20would%20chop%20down%20the%20jackfruits%20from%20the%20trees%2C%20unaware%20of%20the%20value%20they%20would%20bring%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20area%20is%20known%20for%20cardamom%20farming%2C%20and%20like%20other%20farmers%20in%20the%20region%2C%20we%20also%20grew%20jackfruit%20trees%20to%20provide%20shade%20to%20the%20small%20cardamom%20trees.%20Each%20tree%20would%20yield%20between%2010%20and%2050%20jackfruits%2C%20but%20we%20would%20throw%20them%20away%20without%20considering%20their%20potential%20to%20turn%20a%20profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Rani%2C%20jackfruit%20had%20little%20value%20until%202017%2C%20when%20she%20saw%20the%20potential%20in%20the%20plentiful%20resource%20after%20attending%20a%20training%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-13-1729261129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rani%20sources%20jackfru